Name: Lesser Lokir Rune
Types: Rune
Components: Basic Lokir Rune, Level 1 Spell Slot
Description: This rune symbolizes trickery and cunning, allowing those who channel it the ability to manipulate the conniving darkness.SPACESPACEWhile wearing or using an item imbued with this rune, you gain the following feature.SPACETrickster's IreSPACEAs an action, you speak words of malice toward a creature within DISTANCE15-30DISTANCE feet of you that can hear you. Make a ranged spell attack against the target. On a hit, the target takes DAMAGE1-3DAMAGEd10 psychic damage and are blinded with rage, becoming hostile to all creatures for TIME1-3TIME turns. Whenever the target makes an attack roll, it must succeed on a Wisdom saving throw or choose a new target for the attack. If no other target is available, the attack is made against the original target with disadvantage.SPACESPACEYou may invoke this rune a number of times equal to your proficiency bonus before its magic is depleted. The rune will recharge from ambient magic as you complete a long rest. This rune occupies 2 runic attunement slots. Requires Charisma 14 or greater to attune.
